config BR2_PACKAGE_ZFS
        bool "zfs"
        select BR2_PACKAGE_SPL
        help
          The native Linux kernel port of the ZFS filesystem. 
          
          ZFS is a highly scalable future proof file system and logical volume
          manager designed around a few key concepts:
            - Data integrity is paramount.
            - Storage administration should be simple.
            - Everything can be done online.

          http://zfsonlinux.org/